  "description": "<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p811148/\"><img src=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/2009/images/rss_shuangyu.gif\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a><br /><p style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">\n\t<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/zt/bbclearningenglish/\" style=\"font-family: simsun; line-height: 25px;\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://i2.w.hjfile.cn/doc/201507/c6e5c0306433433eb4a3dcf14ae6a467.jpg\" width=\"100%\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">\n\t<img src=\"http://n1image.hjfile.cn/mh/2016/08/29/9720bf00ce5e4797c163888acfde4295.jpg\" /></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">\n\t<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p811148\" title=\"点击获得更好的阅读体验\"><img src=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/2009/images/rss_video.gif\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">\n\t<strong style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">文字稿</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">\n\t<em style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">&ldquo; Microbeads &rdquo;是塑胶微粒，它们常被加入各种产品中起打磨、摩擦的作用。比如，许多化妆品、护肤品和清洁用品中都常含有塑胶微粒。在英国，国会议员建议禁止这些微小塑料颗粒的使用，这是为什么呢？请听 以下 的报道。</em></p>\n<div>\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">Tiny </span><strong style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">fragments</strong><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\"> of plastic </span><strong style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">pervade</strong><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\"> the seas from ocean depth to Arctic ice. They get eaten by small creatures and often </span><strong style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">clog</strong><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\"> their </span><strong style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">gut</strong><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">. </span><strong style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">Shreds of</strong><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\"> plastic can be found in oysters and </span><strong style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">mussels</strong><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">. The small creatures are </span><strong style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">prey</strong><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\"> for bigger animals, so the plastic travels up the </span><strong style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">food chain</strong><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">.</span></div>\n<div>\n\t&nbsp;</div>\n<div>\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">The fragments aren&rsquo;t </span><strong style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">toxic</strong><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\"> themselves, but they attract toxins. The committee says more research is needed to see how much harm they are doing. But the MPs say banning microbeads in </span><strong style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">cosmetics</strong><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\"> would be a small but useful start.</span></div>\n<div>\n\t&nbsp;</div>\n<div>\n\t<strong>词汇表</strong></div>\n<div>\n\t&nbsp;</div>\n<div>\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">fragments 碎粒、碎片</span></div>\n<div>\n\tpervade 遍及、充满</div>\n<div>\n\tclog 堵塞、堵住</div>\n<div>\n\tgut 肠道</div>\n<div>\n\tshreds of 一丝丝的</div>\n<div>\n\tmussels 青口（海鲜产品，一种黑色的贝壳）</div>\n<div>\n\tprey 猎物</div>\n<div>\n\tfood chain 食物链</div>\n<div>\n\ttoxic 有毒的</div>\n<div>\n\ttoxins 毒素</div>\n<div>\n\tcosmetics 化妆品</div>\n<div>\n\t&nbsp;</div>\n<div>\n\t<strong>测验</strong></div>\n<div>\n\t&nbsp;</div>\n<div>\n\t<strong>请听报道并回答下列问题。</strong></div>\n<div>\n\t&nbsp;</div>\n<div>\n\t1. Where in the environment can we find microbeads?</div>\n<div>\n\t&nbsp;</div>\n<div>\n\t2. Which part of a small creature's body do microbeads end up in?</div>\n<div>\n\t&nbsp;</div>\n<div>\n\t3. True or false? Microbeads are toxic.</div>\n<div>\n\t&nbsp;</div>\n<div>\n\t4. Which word is used to mean 'food for a bigger animal or predator'?</div>\n<div>\n\t&nbsp;</div>\n<div>\n\t<strong>答案</strong></div>\n<div>\n\t&nbsp;</div>\n<div>\n\t1. Where in the environment can we find microbeads?</div>\n<div>\n\t<strong>They can be found in the sea.</strong></div>\n<div>\n\t&nbsp;</div>\n<div>\n\t2. Which part of a small creature's body do microbeads end up in?</div>\n<div>\n\t<strong>In their gut.</strong></div>\n<div>\n\t&nbsp;</div>\n<div>\n\t3. True or false? Microbeads are toxic.</div>\n<div>\n\t<strong>False. The microbeads themselves are not toxic, but they attract toxins.</strong></div>\n<div>\n\t&nbsp;</div>\n<div>\n\t4. Which word is used to mean 'food for a bigger animal or predator'?</div>\n<div>\n\t<strong>Prey.</strong></div>\n<p style=\"line-height: 25px;\">\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.hjfile.cn/doc/201507/96d23c9b2d084a4e8c878ed4f9937b90.jpg\" width=\"100%\" /></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 25px;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);\">声明：&nbsp;本文由BBC英语教学授权沪江英语发布。任何媒体禁止转载。</span></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p811148/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p811148\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p808433/\">原来，这些高级词汇竟然出自他们的歌曲</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p810038/\">BBC要拍7部高智商烧脑剧，全是这个女人写的</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p809736/\">学霸的10条特征：看看你中了几条？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p809768/\">《谍影重重5》来了！还有哪些谍战片不容错过</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p807621/\">单身的美好，进入围城的人怎么能懂</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p809991/\">NASA又搞了个大新闻 4.37光年外有另一个地球</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p808460/\">跟中国新歌声学英文：刘雪婧See You Again</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p809700/\">英国奥运健儿回国 取行李时他们都懵逼了……</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p808289/\">美剧经典台词